{"tid":1425028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【初稿，歡迎討論，集思廣益】【每個禮拜 全港罷買】八月十二，正式開始","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T00:14:41.000Z","uid":180201,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b14195908732d166dd0d87b368650f277b3883bf","tid":1425028,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"受此影片啟發：<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190802/59887038?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR03gdpnOe_sCUa7c79QMXvik7CuYijARTdZcnMBOMnTuTPaI_utT9YuvU8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190802%2F59887038%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR03gdpnOe_sCUa7c79QMXvik7CuYijARTdZcnMBOMnTuTPaI_utT9YuvU8&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZt4xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=2a440590\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190802%2F59887038%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR03gdpnOe_sCUa7c79QMXvik7CuYijARTdZcnMBOMnTuTPaI_utT9YuvU8&h=158a8a25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190802/59887038?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR03gdpnOe_sCUa7c79QMXvik7CuYijARTdZcnMBOMnTuTPaI_utT9YuvU8</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">Q: 點解要進行罷買？(目的)</span></em><br />\n全港罷買可以話係零代價嘅抗爭手段 (特別係和理非)，政府可唔可以迫我地去消費？家陣唔買嘢犯法啊？我係窮啊，吹咩？而且罷買極安全，唔洗食催淚彈。唉，依家連買觀星筆都被捕，屈得就屈，仆街黑警。<br />\n<br />\n另外，全港罷買係我地每個市民運用自己應有嘅自由權力去爭取一個更大嘅社會公義，<br />\n可以製造出一個好大嘅壓力比社會，特別係商界，<br />\n希望透過全港罷買去迫使商界向政府談判。<br />\n(其實條link入面嘅片會講得更清楚)<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">Q: 要幾多人響應先有效?</span></em><br />\n根據學者研究，需要當地嘅3.6%人口。以香港而言，只要全港<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">252,000</span></strong>人集中一日唔消費，商家佬就仆硬街了。<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">Q: 每個星期幾進行全港罷買?</span></em><br />\n暫定每個星期一。一步一步，行動會慢慢升級。大家都可以留言討論下可以增加星期幾／點樣進行。例如一三五罷新鴻基嘅商場，二四六罷恆基集團嘅商場。<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">Q: 咁今次運動要爭取訴求?（歡迎理性討論）</span></em><br />\n我覺得爭取到設立獨立調查委員會追究黑警由6月9至今嘅所有責任(開槍責任、警黑合作、性暴力、不成比例嘅暴力對待示威者/百姓等等)，就有機會從過程中爭取到其他訴求，如撤銷所有暴動定性、不檢控及釋放示威者。當然，亦歡迎大家討論應唔應該利用全港罷買集中設立獨立調查委員會追究黑警由6月9至今嘅所有責任，抑或轉做五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇？<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望可以集思廣益，令全港罷買獲得重大成功。<br />\n<br />\n文宣初稿 (希望有手足可以幫忙設計張更好)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eFrzcDy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeFrzcDy.png&h=e378612b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c391fc572bdd831a71ce8909de2ab4c4e41280a","tid":1425028,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"153d81bd29caa04aa837fa7a98869ecb95c5cb20","tid":1425028,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e69b714caf51eebda54e357bd256e84f1bbb9c3","tid":1425028,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2250ad2e056620b39d51074d11ef282e4f6f51ae","tid":1425028,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:36:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a01322e242839aad765f50a7b3a7ef8e69def44","tid":1425028,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:36:34.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"352bdd4af3c539d35ac7427fc818e368b3e478ac","tid":1425028,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ebda5